---
title: Sweet Chili Paneer with Veggies and Green Onion Rice
description: Tonight, we're bringing you a vibrant and bright version of sweet chili paneer. Served over nutty and fluffy basmati rice studded with savoury green onions, this meal is comfort in a bowl!
